  "title": "Senior / Radiographer",
  "description": "<p><strong>What’s on Offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mission: Provide compassionate, excellent and holistic healthcare. Tagline:- <strong>Serve all with Love.</strong></li>\n  <li>Company: Guided by Catholic values, as a missionary not-for-profit hospital, we reach out and serve all our patients and visitors with love, continue to make private healthcare accessible to our community by providing reasonable price points and bill transparency. We continue to be progressive to better serve current and future generations.</li>\n  <li>Values: <strong>Compassion, Humility, Integrity, Respect and Peace (CHIRP).</strong></li>\n  <li>Work Satisfaction: An impactful role in shaping a high performing &amp; engaging culture.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Who We Need</strong></p>\n<p>The Radiographer performs diagnostic imaging services, including CT scans, Ultrasound, Mammography, BMD, Fluoroscopy, and Theatre Radiography</p>\n<p>Your key responsibilities are:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provides radiography services in the Diagnostic Imaging Department.</li>\n  <li>Conducts special examinations such as CT Scan, Ultrasound, Mammography, BMD, Fluoroscopy and Theatre Radiography.</li>\n  <li>Liaises with and accepts advice from the Manager.</li>\n  <li>Assists the Radiologist and doctors in the imaging process.</li>\n  <li>Assists in the care and maintenance of Ultrasound and X-ray machines and radiographic equipment.</li>\n  <li>Participates in departmental activities such as quality assurance and performance appraisal.</li>\n  <li>Attends and contributes to departmental staff meetings.</li>\n  <li>Supervises and directs activities of departmental staff when necessary.</li>\n  <li>Participates in on-call duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>How to Succeed</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor of Science in Radiography or Diploma from College of Radiographers (UK) or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Registered with AHPC.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of clinical experience in an acute hospital.</li>\n  <li>Computer literacy.</li>\n  <li>To cover on call duties as rostered.</li>\n  <li>Office hours, off on Sunday and PH.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Key Highlights</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Free Shuttle bus service from Bishan &amp; Caldecott MRT Stations.</li>\n  <li>Subsidised staff meals.</li>\n  <li>Work for an organisation that gives back to the community.</li>\n</ul>",
